===2020 census===
As of the [[2020 United States census|2020 census]], Arion had a population of 97 people, with 47 households and 28 families residing in the city.<ref name="Census2020DP">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Demographic Profile (DP1)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/dp?get=NAME,DP1_0021P,DP1_0024P,DP1_0025C,DP1_0049C,DP1_0045C,DP1_0069C,DP1_0073C,DP1_0125P,DP1_0126P,DP1_0129P,DP1_0133P,DP1_0137P,DP1_0138P,DP1_0139P,DP1_0141P,DP1_0142P,DP1_0143P,DP1_0145P,DP1_0146P,DP1_0147C,DP1_0148C,DP1_0149C,DP1_0156C,DP1_0157C,DP1_0158C,DP1_0159P,DP1_0160P&for=place%3A02755&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2021|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref><ref name="Census2020PL">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Redistricting Data (Public Law 94-171)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/pl?get=NAME,P1_001N,P1_003N,P1_004N,P1_005N,P1_006N,P1_007N,P1_008N,P1_009N,P2_001N,P2_002N,H1_001N,H1_002N&for=place%3A02755&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2021|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref> The [[population density]] was 195.5 inhabitants per square mile (75.5/km<sup>2</sup>). There were 47 housing units at an average density of 94.7 per square mile (36.6/km<sup>2</sup>).<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

The median age was 40.4 years. 23.7% of residents were under the age of 18 and 21.6% were 65 years of age or older. 27.8% of residents were under the age of 20; 7.2% were between the ages of 20 and 24; 22.7% were from 25 to 44; and 20.6% were from 45 to 64. For every 100 females there were 136.6 males, and for every 100 females age 18 and over there were 146.7 males age 18 and over. The gender makeup of the city was 57.7% male and 42.3% female.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

All residents lived in rural areas.<ref name="Census2020DHC">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Demographic and Housing Characteristics (DHC)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/dhc?get=NAME,P2_002N,P2_003N&for=place%3A02755&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2023|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref>

Of the 47 households, 27.7% had children under the age of 18 living with them. Of all households, 46.8% were married-couple households, 10.6% were cohabiting-couple households, 27.7% were households with a male householder and no spouse or partner present, and 14.9% were households with a female householder and no spouse or partner present. 40.4% of households were non-families, 29.8% were made up of individuals, and 8.5% had someone living alone who was 65 years of age or older.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

There were 47 housing units, of which 0.0% were vacant. The homeowner vacancy rate was 0.0% and the rental vacancy rate was 0.0%.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

